}}'''阿卜杜拉·艾哈迈德·阿卜杜拉'''（{{lang-ar|أبو محمد المصري}}，{{bd|1963年|6月6日|2020年|8月7日}}）是[[基地组织|基地组织]]內一名來自[[埃及|埃及]]的高级成员。他因被指控參與[[1998年美国大使馆爆炸案|1998年美国大使馆爆炸案]]而被美国通缉。他被視为[[基地组织|基地组织]]內最有经验的[[恐怖活動|恐怖活動]]策划者以及该组织的二把手<ref name="indicted">{{cite web|url=http://cns.miis.edu/pubs/reports/pdfs/binladen/indict.pdf |format=PDF |title=Copy of indictment - ''USA v. Usama bin Laden et al.'' |work=Center for Nonproliferation Studies, [[明德大学蒙特雷国际研究学院|明德大学蒙特雷国际研究学院]] |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20011110104742/http://cns.miis.edu/pubs/reports/pdfs/binladen/indict.pdf |archivedate=2001-11-10 }}</ref><ref name="fbiAAA">[https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/terrorists/terabdullah.htm Wanted poster on AAA] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161222172714/https://www2.fbi.gov/wanted/terrorists/terabdullah.htm |date=2016-12-22 }}, [[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]], US Department of Justice</ref>。

美國情报人员表示，阿卜杜拉2003年在伊朗被拘禁，但2015年起在[[德黑兰|德黑兰]]卻可以自由活动<ref>{{cite news |title=窝藏“基地”“二号人物”？ 伊朗指美国“栽赃” |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/431915773_267106 |publisher=新華社 |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116210639/https://www.sohu.com/a/431915773_267106 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年11月，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》报道称，应美国要求下，以色列特工於當年8月在[[伊朗|伊朗]]將阿卜杜拉杀害<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/13/world/middleeast/al-masri-abdullah-qaeda-dead.html|title=Al Qaeda’s No. 2, Accused in U.S. Embassy Attacks, Is Secretly Killed in Iran|first1=Adam|last1=Goldman|first2=Eric|last2=Schmitt|first3=Farnaz|last3=Fassihi|first4=Ronen|last4=Bergman|date=2020-11-14|via=NYTimes.com|access-date=2020-11-15|archive-date=2021-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210710195700/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/13/world/middleeast/al-masri-abdullah-qaeda-dead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该报道未得到美国或以色列官员的公开证实，伊朗也予以否认<ref name="#1"/>。2021年1月12日，美國國務卿[[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]證實阿卜杜拉已死。<ref name=":2">{{cite news|last=Jakes|first=Lara|last2=Schmitt|first2=Eric|last3=Barnes|first3=Julian E.|date=2021-01-12|title=Pompeo Says Iran Is New Base for Al Qaeda, but Offers Little Proof|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/12/us/politics/pompeo-iran-qaeda-terror.html|access-date=2021-01-12|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124162943/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/12/us/politics/pompeo-iran-qaeda-terror.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite news|date=2021-01-12|title=Pompeo Confirms Death of Al-Qaeda’s No. 2 in Tehran Last August|language=en|work=Bloomberg.com|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-12/pompeo-confirms-death-of-al-qaeda-s-no-2-in-tehran-last-august|access-date=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121230233/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-12/pompeo-confirms-death-of-al-qaeda-s-no